    public final class Over<S,T,A,B>
extends Object
implements Fn3<Lens<S,T,A,B>,Function<? super A,? extends B>,S,T>
    Given a lens, a function from A to B, and a "larger" value S, produce a T by retrieving the A from the S, applying the function, and updating the S with the B resulting from the function.

    This function is similar to Set, except that it allows the setting value B to be derived from S via function application, rather than provided.

    See Also:
    Set, View
